  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated potatoes </strong>and <strong>grated carrot</strong> to the middle of a tea towel and bring the four corners together to form a ball, twist the ball and squeeze out as much of the liquid as you can</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1652714271852-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1652714271852-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1652714271852-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1652714271852-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1652714271852-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>squeezed</strong> <strong>potato </strong>and <strong>carrot</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> and mix it all together – this is your<strong> rösti</strong> <strong>mix</strong></p><p>Divide the<strong> rösti</strong> <strong>mix</strong> into 3 portions per person and add them to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or 2!)</p><p>Place a separate piece of <strong>baking paper</strong> over the röstis, press down with an additional baking tray to flatten them, then put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 20 min or until the röstis are beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1652714281297-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1652714281297-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1652714281297-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1652714281297-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1652714281297-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1652714290208-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1652714290208-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1652714290208-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1652714290208-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1652714290208-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and discard the baking paper covering the röstis</p><p>Return the tray to the oven and cook for a further 5-6 min or until crispy and golden – these are your<strong> crispy carrot röstis</strong></p><p>Once cooked, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652714298170-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652714298170-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652714298170-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652714298170-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652714298170-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the röstis are cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s]</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652714305288-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652714305288-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652714305288-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652714305288-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652714305288-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred it finely</p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>chopped shallots </strong>and <strong>sliced radishes</strong></p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> then toss – this is your <strong>radish</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652714313396-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652714313396-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652714313396-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
